    "Furthermore, they contribute a comprehensive classification system, aligning specific security threats with the corresponding components of the Cisco IoT reference model to provide a holistic understanding of the potential vulnerabilities in the IoT ecosystem.",
    "The progress in machine learning and deep learning has opened up new possibilities for creating potent techniques to enhance Internet of Things security.",
    "The primary objective of [43] is to conduct an in-depth review of comprehensive studies in this domain.",
    "Additionally, it furnishes an extensive compilation of the attributes and obstacles associated with utilizing machine learning and deep learning to secure the Internet of Things frameworks.",
